{"id":91695,"date":"2017-09-11T19:57:29","date_gmt":"2017-09-11T23:57:29","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/techvibes.com\/?p=91695"},"modified":"2017-09-14T13:51:32","modified_gmt":"2017-09-14T17:51:32","slug":"killer-spaces-clio-vancouver","status":"publish","type":"magazine","link":"https:\/\/brainstation.io\/magazine\/killer-spaces-clio-vancouver","title":{"rendered":"Clio&#8217;s Cutting-Edge Vancouver Headquarters"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Clio was inspired by co-founders&#8217; Jack Newton and Rian Gauvreau simple desire to build a tool that improved someone\u2019s life.<\/p>\n<p>A decade ago, following conversations with the Law Society of British Columbia, the pair discovered the legal industry lacked the innovative and affordable software to manage case files. They had their business idea, and after an intensive period of development, they had a solution: a cloud-based software that would help lawyers cut down on administrative overhead while boosting their productivity.<\/p>\n<p>Clio launched in October 2008 with the first-to-market cloud-based legal case and practice management platform\u2014saving lawyers highly prized billable hours. The software integrates with dozens of popular desktop and mobile applications, helping law firms with key tasks to smoothly run their practice.<\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-91774\" src=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100113\/Clio-Office-6.jpg\" alt=\"Clio Office-6\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100113\/Clio-Office-6.jpg 1500w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100113\/Clio-Office-6-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100113\/Clio-Office-6-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100113\/Clio-Office-6-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100113\/Clio-Office-6-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Today, Newton holds the CEO title and Gauvreau is the company\u2019s Chief People Officer. Headquartered in the Vancouver suburb Burnaby, the co-founders lead a 200 person company that includes offices in Toronto and Dublin. Clio\u2019s clients, however are truly global, with customers in over 80 countries. The company offers their software to law students for free at more than 150 institutions in the U.S.\u2013including 13 of the country\u2019s top 20 law schools. Since launch, Clio has worked with over 50 bar associations and has even reached exclusive agreements with state bar associations in New York, Texas and Illinois.<\/p>\n<h2>Work<\/h2>\n<p>Clio moved to their bright Burnaby office in 2012. The colorful custom wallpaper catches attention with a design that reflects B.C.\u2019s beautiful outdoors and the city\u2019s west coast lifestyle. Both office floors have wrap around windows that offer a 360 view of the city\u2019s skylines and nearby mountains.<\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-91775\" src=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100113\/Clio-Office-7.jpg\" alt=\"Clio Office-7\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100113\/Clio-Office-7.jpg 1500w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100113\/Clio-Office-7-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100113\/Clio-Office-7-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100113\/Clio-Office-7-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100113\/Clio-Office-7-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ssdg.com\/\" target=\"_blank\">SSDG Interior Designers<\/a>\u00a0worked with Clio to create the open-concept workspace. The office design won the firm the Interior Design Institute of BC&#8217;s Award of Merit.<\/p>\n<p>The Burnaby team includes product development, business operations, product management, people operations, sales, customer experience, marketing, and production engineering.\u00a0Monitors throughout\u00a0the office showcase Clio data, metric dashboards and social notices, so that everyone shares common company goals.<\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-91782\" src=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100113\/Clio-Office-14.jpg\" alt=\"Clio Office-14\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100113\/Clio-Office-14.jpg 1500w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100113\/Clio-Office-14-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100113\/Clio-Office-14-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100113\/Clio-Office-14-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100113\/Clio-Office-14-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>The office features a range of workstations that champion ergonomics. Clio wanted the open space to foster cross-team communication, so the office has designated \u201chuddle zones\u201d to encourage brief, collaborative stand up meetings. There\u2019s not a single private office.<\/p>\n<blockquote><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u201cWe wanted an office space that reflected our culture. Our teams work in open concepts with their leadership by their side. We also made sure to \u00a0have a variety of collaborative spaces for everyone to make use of.\u201d \u2014 Jack Newton, CEO and co-founder of Clio<\/span><\/p><\/blockquote>\n<p>Meeting rooms on the upper level are named after B.C.&#8217;s famous mountains like Whistler and Blackcomb, while the lower level spaces bear the names of provincial lakes.<\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-91777\" src=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100113\/Clio-Office-9.jpg\" alt=\"Clio Office-9\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100113\/Clio-Office-9.jpg 1500w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100113\/Clio-Office-9-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100113\/Clio-Office-9-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100113\/Clio-Office-9-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100113\/Clio-Office-9-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>The\u00a0design of the\u00a0<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">space\u00a0reflects Clio&#8217;s founding value: <em>No Doors, Only Windows.<\/em>\u201d As such, there are no walled off rooms and the\u00a0meeting rooms are clear glass. <\/span><\/p>\n<p>Each floor has its own lounge complete with a large kitchen. One was designed for community building and communication, where as the other embodies a cozy living room with big comfy couches and chairs.<\/p>\n<h2>Food<\/h2>\n<p>Clio employees\u2014dubbed Clions\u2014have their pick of an array of breakfast foods every day of the week and are treated to a catered lunch each Friday. The company also offers opt-in lunches, subsidized by Clio at a small fee. Stocked snacks meet all tastes and palates, including energy bars, fruit and vegetables, roasted chickpeas and candy.\u00a0In warmer months, employees migrate to the building&#8217;s\u00a0<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">outdoor deck equipped with a BBQ.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-91773\" src=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100113\/Clio-Office-5.jpg\" alt=\"Clio Office-5\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100113\/Clio-Office-5.jpg 1500w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100113\/Clio-Office-5-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100113\/Clio-Office-5-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100113\/Clio-Office-5-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100113\/Clio-Office-5-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-91769\" src=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100114\/Clio-Office-1.jpg\" alt=\"Clio Office-1\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100114\/Clio-Office-1.jpg 1500w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100114\/Clio-Office-1-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100114\/Clio-Office-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100114\/Clio-Office-1-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100114\/Clio-Office-1-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>When\u00a0the Clio team has to buckle down to meet company goals, dinners are ordered to keep the team fuelled. After successfully buckling down, wine and beer are also on tap to help Clions unwind.<\/p>\n<p>Supplying quality coffee was especially important for the founders. Clio sources coffee from\u00a0local <a href=\"https:\/\/49thcoffee.com\/\" target=\"_blank\">49th Parallel<\/a>,\u00a0brewed on both floors at barista stations what whip up your morning fuel in any style you may want<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_91779\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-91779\" style=\"width: 1500px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img class=\"wp-image-91779 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100113\/Clio-Office-11.jpg\" alt=\"Clio Office-11\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100113\/Clio-Office-11.jpg 1500w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100113\/Clio-Office-11-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100113\/Clio-Office-11-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100113\/Clio-Office-11-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100113\/Clio-Office-11-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-91779\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Care for a side of puzzle with your afternoon tea?<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2>Culture<\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Clio has values-based small groups\u00a0dubbed \u201cMinistries&#8221; that are dedicated to solving organization growing pains, including streamlining inter-departmental communications.\u00a0<\/span>Each Friday, Clio has an all hands meeting to review ongoing business and state of affairs.<\/p>\n<blockquote><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u201cCollaboration is at the core of everything we do at Clio. We are a very transparent company and meet weekly to discuss business developments. At the root of it, we are Team Clio; we work hard and have a lot of fun in the process.\u201d \u2014 Jack Newton, CEO and co-founder of Clio<\/span><\/p><\/blockquote>\n<p>Clions can make use of free gym memberships, weekly in-house yoga classes, and instructor-led boot camp\u00a0classes to stay fit and healthy.\u00a0Naturopaths,\u00a0massage therapists and acupuncturists are also brought into the office every month for some blissful relaxation.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_91783\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-91783\" style=\"width: 1500px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img class=\"wp-image-91783 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100111\/Clio-Office-15.jpg\" alt=\"Clio Office-15\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100111\/Clio-Office-15.jpg 1500w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100111\/Clio-Office-15-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100111\/Clio-Office-15-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100111\/Clio-Office-15-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100111\/Clio-Office-15-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-91783\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Some people say the eighth chakra is sound legal management&#8230; Specifically, these people.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Employees also can tap into traditional benefits including\u00a0RRSP-matching, parental leave options for both moms and dads, and generous\u00a0time off.<\/p>\n<p>A bus\u00a0shuttles Clions directly to work from the Skytrain station, taking away some of the stress of a morning commute. If employees choose to ride on two wheels to the office, the building provides end of trip facilities\u00a0including bike lockers and showers.<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The company also hosts an Annual Team Day at the Burnaby office where employees from global locations travel to B.C. for a few days to discuss all things Clio as well as <\/span>team-building activities. The trip wraps up with the company&#8217;s holiday party.<\/p>\n<h2>Education<\/h2>\n<p>Clio values personal and professional employee development. The company sponsors educational courses and provides staff with materials to support their learning.<\/p>\n<p>Top Clio performers are honoured by being chosen to participate in the annual Clio Cloud Conference,\u00a0the top\u00a0legal technology conference\u00a0in North America.<\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-91772\" src=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100114\/Clio-Office-4.jpg\" alt=\"Clio Office-4\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100114\/Clio-Office-4.jpg 1500w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100114\/Clio-Office-4-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100114\/Clio-Office-4-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100114\/Clio-Office-4-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100114\/Clio-Office-4-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Lunch and learns are regularly hosted at the office&#8217;s communal spaces, and an employee-initiated Speaker Club\u00a0provides a forum for staff to improve their presentation skills.\u00a0Clio also runs\u00a0lightning talks where employees can share their skills, specialties and insider knowledge with the whole team.<\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-91786\" src=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100111\/Clio-Office-18.jpg\" alt=\"Clio Office-18\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100111\/Clio-Office-18.jpg 1500w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100111\/Clio-Office-18-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100111\/Clio-Office-18-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100111\/Clio-Office-18-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100111\/Clio-Office-18-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>The internal performance coach\u00a0is currently working with Clio&#8217;s people leaders to accelerate their development, but\u00a0soon anyone will be able to\u00a0book an appointment to privately discuss anything from development goals or obstacles they wish to overcome.<\/p>\n<h2>Fun<\/h2>\n<p>Anyone can join employee-led groups, from an after-work dinner club\u00a0to \u201cdawn patrol,\u201d a group of early morning climbers\u00a0who tackle the infamous\u00a0Grouse Mountain.\u00a0Clio also\u00a0has a community softball team and battles their building neighbours on the volleyball courts in the summer.<\/p>\n<p>Clions have also become known for pulling pranks, including\u00a0gift wrapping the co-founders\u2019 furniture and also replacing their\u00a0furniture with children-sized replicas.<\/p>\n<p>In the dog-friendly office, employees can have some midday fun with video games, board games, table tennis and foosball.<\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-91771\" src=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100114\/Clio-Office-3.jpg\" alt=\"Clio Office-3\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100114\/Clio-Office-3.jpg 1500w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100114\/Clio-Office-3-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100114\/Clio-Office-3-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100114\/Clio-Office-3-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100114\/Clio-Office-3-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\" \/><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_91781\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-91781\" style=\"width: 1500px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img class=\"wp-image-91781 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100113\/Clio-Office-13.jpg\" alt=\"Clio Office-13\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100113\/Clio-Office-13.jpg 1500w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100113\/Clio-Office-13-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100113\/Clio-Office-13-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100113\/Clio-Office-13-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2017\/09\/13100113\/Clio-Office-13-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-91781\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Believe it or not, this is Ripley.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h6 style=\"text-align: right;\">Photos by Matt Odynski<\/h6>\n<p>Do you have an amazing office and would like to be featured here? Get in touch with us: contact@techvibes.com.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Clio was inspired by co-founders&#8217; Jack Newton and Rian Gauvreau simple desire to build a tool that improved someone\u2019s life. A decade ago, following conversations with the Law Society of British Columbia, the pair discovered the legal industry lacked the innovative and affordable software to manage case files. They had their business idea, and after &hellip; <a href=\"https:\/\/brainstation.io\/magazine\/killer-spaces-clio-vancouver\">Continued<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":76241,"featured_media":91778,"menu_order":0,"template":"","meta":[],"categories":[13],"tags":[1314,731,1319,1320,22],"magazine-series":[48],"magazine-region":[428],"magazine-topic":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/brainstation.io\/wp\/api\/wp\/v2\/magazine\/91695"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/brainstation.io\/wp\/api\/wp\/v2\/magazine"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/brainstation.io\/wp\/api\/wp\/v2\/types\/magazine"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/brainstation.io\/wp\/api\/wp\/v2\/users\/76241"}],"version-history":[{"co